MERCY KITOMARI: In Tanzania.

00:04:29.090 --> 00:04:29.840
LAURA LING: In all Tanzania?

00:04:29.840 --> 00:04:30.970
MERCY KITOMARI: Yeah.

00:04:30.970 --> 00:04:33.440
LAURA LING: Why do you think
that there are some few.

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:34.880
MERCY KITOMARI: The costs.

00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:38.440
An average person won't even
think of doing this business

00:04:38.440 --> 00:04:41.595
because when they
think of power cuts,

00:04:41.595 --> 00:04:43.620
you don't even think
following that.

